[I] A Python interface for PostgreSQL

[T] PyGreSQL is a Python module that interfaces to a PostgreSQL database.
[T] It embeds the PostgreSQL query library to allow easy use of the powerful
[T] PostgreSQL features from a Python script.

[U] https://www.pygresql.org

